She looked at Black Aracnia and then to Quickstrike. "No, my logic 
circuits aren't fried.  If Megatron can't see or hear us, we may 
still have a chance to get out of here with our skins on."  She 
looked at Black Aracnia,"I didn't mean to just fly off the handle 
wuite the way I did.  But I wanted megatron to thing I had lost it. 
I'd never go against you Black Aracnia, You are my friend.  I'd never 
turn on you."  She looked over at Quickstrike.  She smiled, "Sorry, I 
did what I thought would buy us a few minutes.  And that's all we may 
have."  She looked around,"Well? Let's go! Megatron had already let 
us know he isn't pleased with us, so let's scram out of here."
